prod.desciption: Grab a pack of coffee beans to match the Jordan 1 Retro High Travis Scott. This AJ1 comes with a brown upper plus white accents, black Nike "Swoosh", sail midsole, and a brown sole. These sneakers released in May 2019 and retailed for $175. Mess the club up in these after buying them on StockX.
